<h2>
  <p style="color: #1a0080;"> Background </p>
</h2>

<p>I started learning to program in Java with the help of interactive coding courses such as codeacademy and coursera. I was able to create mini projects 
 in Java, which helped me to develop knowledge on how this programming language works.</p>

<h2>
  <p style="color: #1a0080;"> Features </p>
</h2>
We can choose the Java language for many reasons:
<ul>
<li>It is platform-independent (Write Once, Run Anywhere)</li>
<li>Supports object-oriented programming</li>
<li>Supports a diverse range of libraries and frameworks</li>
</ul>

<h2><p style="color: #1a0080;"> Comparison </p> </h2>

